title: 2.41 Jesus' Disciples II: The Other Guys
itunes:title: Jesus' Disciples II: The Other Guys
description: After the Big Three disciples come the forgettable bit-players, the Nondescript Nine: Andrew, Philip, Bartholomew (also known as Nathaniel), Matthew, Thomas Didymus, James son of Alphaeus, Judas (also known as Thaddaeus), Simon the Cananaean, and Judas Iscariot.
